      "writtenOn": "2026-06-06T04:53:11Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Taking the shared_ptr by value + std::move is the recommended sink idiom: an rvalue moves in with no refcount bump, an lvalue copies once (same as const-ref + copy). Happy to switch if you\u0027d still prefer it.",
